20worry%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20one%20of%20us%20gets%20into%20a%20serious%20relationship%20or%20needs%20to%20move.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Issy%20Packer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-house-together-twin-sister-cold-feet-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doctor%20Assaulted%20After%20Woman%20Claims%20She%20Was%20Inappropriately%20Touched%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20has%20been%20assaulted%20in%20Karnataka's%20Vijayapura%20allegedly%20for%20inappropriately%20touching%20a%20woman%20during%20a%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20patient%2C%20who%20was%20pregnant%2C%20underwent%20a%20scan%20at%20the%20Vijayapura%20District%20Hospital%20on%20April%209.%20Later%2C%20she%20reportedly%20told%20her%20husband%20that%20the%20doctor%20had%20touched%20her%20inappropriately%20during%20the%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%20and%20his%20friend%20barged%20into%20the%20hospital%20and%20assaulted%20the%20doctor%2C%20a%20postgraduate%20student%20of%20radiology.%20The%20doctor%2C%20however%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20doing%20his%20job%20and%20denied%20any%20inappropriate%20behaviour%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20sparked%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20doctors%20inside%20the%20hospital.%20They%20demanded%20security%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20possible%20to%20conduct%20the%20scan%20without%20touching%20the%20woman.%20Medical%20services%20were%20hit%20for%20couple%20of%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20investigating%20the%20matter.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744549980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fjdl061jk_karnataka-hospital_625x300_13_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-doctor-assaulted-after-woman-claims-she-was-inappropriately-touched-8155394%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20doctor%20has%20been%20assaulted%20in%20Karnataka's%20Vijayapura%20allegedly%20for%20inappropriately%20touching%20a%20woman%20during%20a%20scan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20First%20Futuristic%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20Laser%20Weapon%20Shoots%20Down%20Drone%20Swarm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20successfully%20tested%20a%20futuristic%20weapon%20for%20the%20first%20time%20by%20using%20high-powered%20laser-based%20directed%20energy%20to%20shoot%20down%20a%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20made%20by%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20tracked%20the%20drone%2C%20fired%20a%20laser%20beam%20and%20destroyed%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20platform%20is%20a%20game-changing%20one%20for%20India's%20armed%20forces%20as%20drone%20warfare%20is%20increasingly%20being%20used%20in%20modern%20combat%2C%20such%20as%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCHESS%20DRDO%20conducted%20a%20successful%20field%20demonstration%20of%20the%20Land%20version%20of%20Vehicle%20mounted%20Laser%20Directed%20Weapon(DEW)%20MK-II(A)%20at%20Kurnool%20today.%20It%20defeated%20the%20fixed%20wing%20UAV%20and%20Swarm%20Drones%20successfully%20causing%20structural%20damage%20and%20disabled%20the%20surveillance%20sensors.%20With%20this%20successful%20trial%20country%20has%20joined%20the%20exclusive%20club%20of%20the%20Global%20powers%20who%20possess%20the%20high%20power%20Laser%20DEW%20System%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRDO%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20puts%20India%20in%20the%20exclusive%20group%20of%20nations%20with%20high-power%20Laser-DEW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20I%20know%2C%20it%20is%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%20and%20China%20that%20have%20demonstrated%20this%20capability.%20Israel%20is%20also%20working%20on%20similar%20capabilities%2C%20I%20would%20say%20we%20are%20the%20fourth%20or%20fifth%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20demonstrate%20this%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20DRDO%20Chairman%20Samir%20V%20Kamat%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamat%20said%20this%20is%20just%20the%20%26quot%3Bbeginning%20of%20the%20journey%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20DRDO%20is%20working%20on%20a%20number%20of%20technologies%20%26quot%3Bthat%20will%20give%20us%20Star%20Wars%20capability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20journey.%20The%20synergy%20that%20this%20lab%20has%20achieved%20with%20other%20DRDO%20labs%2C%20industry%20and%20academia%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20we%20will%20reach%20our%20destination%20soon...%20We%20are%20also%20working%20on%20other%20high%20energy%20systems%20like%20high%20energy%20microwaves%2C%20electromagnetic%20pulse.%20So%20we%20are%20working%20on%20a%20number%20of%20technologies%20that%20will%20give%20us%20Star%20Wars%20capability.%20What%20you%20saw%20today%20was%20one%20of%20the%20components%20of%20Star%20Wars%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kamat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECHESS%20DRDO%20conducted%20a%20successful%20field%20demonstration%20of%20the%20Land%20version%20of%20Vehicle%20mounted%20Laser%20Directed%20Weapon(DEW)%20MK-II(A)%20at%20Kurnool%20today.%20It%20defeated%20the%20fixed%20wing%20UAV%20and%20Swarm%20Drones%20successfully%20causing%20structural%20damage%20and%20disable%20the%20surveillance%20sensors.%20With...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FU1jaIurZco%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FU1jaIurZco%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20DRDO%20(%40DRDO_India)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDRDO_India%2Fstatus%2F1911393160044904900%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2013%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indigenously%20designed%20and%20developed%20Mk-II(A)%20DEW%20system%20was%20demonstrated%20in%20its%20entire%20spectrum%20of%20capability%20by%20engaging%20fixed-wing%20drones%20at%20long%20range%2C%20thwarting%20a%20multiple%20drone%20attack%20and%20destroying%20enemy%20surveillance%20sensors%20and%20antennae.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lightning%20speed%20of%20engagement%2C%20the%20precision%20and%20the%20lethality%20delivered%20to%20the%20target%20within%20a%20few%20seconds%20made%20it%20the%20most%20potent%20counter%20drone%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDRDO's%20Centre%20for%20High%20Energy%20Systems%20and%20Sciences%20(CHESS)%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20developed%20the%20system%20along%20with%20LRDE%2C%20IRDE%2C%20DLRL%20and%20academic%20institutions%20and%20Indian%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20detected%20by%20a%20radar%20or%20by%20its%20inbuilt%20electro%20optic%20(EO)%20system%2C%20the%20laser-DEW%20can%20engage%20targets%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20light%20and%20use%20an%20intense%20beam%20of%20powerful%20light%20(laser%20beam)%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20target%2C%20leading%20to%20structural%20failure%20or%20more%20impactful%20results%20if%20the%20warhead%20is%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20cutting-edge%20weaponry%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20revolutionise%20the%20battlespace%20by%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20expensive%20ammunition%20while%20also%20lowering%20the%20risk%20of%20collateral%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proliferation%20of%20unmanned%20aerial%20systems%20(UAS)%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20drone%20swarms%20as%20asymmetric%20threats%20are%20driving%20the%20demand%20for%20directed%20energy%20weapons%20with%20counter-UAS%20and%20counter-swarm%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DEW%20will%20replace%20traditional%20kinetic%20weapons%20and%20missile%20defence%20systems%20due%20to%20its%20ease%20of%20operation%20and%20cost-effectiveness.%20The%20requirement%20for%20cost-effective%20defence%20solutions%20to%20offset%20the