C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20turned%20the%20world%20upside%20down.%20I%20still%20had%20no%20viable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-internship-converting-full-time-job-offer-advice-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-time%20job%20offers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20table.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20market%20felt%20uncertain%20like%20many%20other%20things%20at%20that%20time.%20I%20assumed%20the%20worst%20outcomes%20for%20my%20work%20prospects%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20opposite%20reality%20bore%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20people%20home%2C%20isolated%2C%20and%20glued%20to%20their%20screens%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20digital%20content%20seemed%20to%20soar%2C%20lifting%20my%20writing%20business%20right%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWork%20picked%20up%20steam%20until%20I%20was%20so%20booked%20I%20could%20pass%20on%20gigs%20that%20paid%20less%20and%20didn't%20feel%20very%20rewarding.%20I%20started%20really%20taking%20pleasure%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffreelance-writer-failed-went-back-full-time-job-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-time%20freelance%20writing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20I%20began%20developing%20a%20brand%20identity%2C%20reading%20books%20for%20writing%20professionals%2C%20and%20enrolling%20in%20virtual%20conferences%20and%20classes%20for%20freelancers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20while%2C%20I%20felt%20enriched%20by%20my%20work%20and%20everything%20I%20was%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c047e9d8-2a22-4b98-9320-207b4460c338%5C%22%3EEventually%2C%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20I%20loved%20my%20remade%20professional%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20about%20a%20year%2C%20my%20business%20was%20booming%2C%20and%20I%20was%20even%20making%20more%20money%20than%20I'd%20made%20as%20a%20corporate%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20thriving%20in%20a