retailers%20pass%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadditional%20costs%20down%20to%20the%20consumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-built-elite-secrets-bridal-made-247000-last-year-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBridal%20retailers%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20tariffs%20have%20been%20a%20huge%20disruption%20to%20their%20industry.%20The%20National%20Bridal%20Retailers%20Association%2C%20which%20represents%20over%206%2C000%20independent%20brick-and-mortar%20bridal%20stores%20around%20the%20United%20States%2C%20said%20as%20many%20as%2090%25%20of%20bridal%20gowns%20are%20produced%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overriding%20feeling%20is%20despair%2C%26quot%3B%20Angie%20Oven%2C%20a%20bridal%20shop%20owner%20and%20president%20of%20the%20NBRA%2C%20told%20BI%20after%20a%20meeting%20she%20held%20with%2075%20of%20the%20group's%20members.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20PTSD%20right%20now%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20us%20really%20just%20recovered%20from%20COVID.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOven%2C%20who%20owns%20The%20Bridal%20Gallery%20in%20Salem%2C%20Oregon%2C%20said%20shops%20are%20working%20closely%20with%20manufacturers%20to%20find%20solutions.%20The%20group%20is%20also%20appealing%20to%20lawmakers%20to%20push%20for%20bridal%20gowns%20to%20be%20added%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-news-tech-sector-trump-announces-tariff-exemptions-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff%20exemption%20list%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20No.%201%20goal%20is%20to%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20tariff%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandra%20Gonzalez%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20NBRA%20and%20owner%20of%20Sparkle%20Bridal%20Couture%20in%20Sacramento%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Americans%20often%20associate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-retail-forever-21-billabong-bankruptcy-retail-cheap-shopping-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20with%20cheap%20goods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bridal%20shop%20owners%20said%20the%20quality%20of%20dresses%20produced%20in%20China%20at%20scale%20is%20remarkable%2C%20from%20the%20lace%20to%20the%20boning%20to%20the%20sometimes%2010%2C000%20beads%20handsewn%20onto%20the%20gowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20the%20infrastructure%20to%20produce%20the%20quality%20of%20goods%20that%20brides%20are%20demanding%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Gonzalez%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20build%20the%20factories%20and%20train%20the%20people%2C%20that%20would%20take%20a%20whole%20generation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3ff180b-b00c-487c-8c08-b3cddd96d2aa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%20increases%20and%20uncertainty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlicia%20Adams%2C%20owner%20of%20Her's%20Bridal%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Occasion%20in%20Minden%2C%20Louisiana%2C%20said%20the%20price%20of%20gowns%20is%20already%20going%20up.%20Some%20manufacturers%20are%20raising%20the%20wholesale%20price%20of%20gowns%20by%20as%20much%20as%2030%25%2C%20while%20others%20are%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now%2C%20trying%20to%20absorb%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20it's%20over%20100%25%2C%20obviously%20those%20manufacturers%20and%20designers%20aren't%20able%20to%20absorb%20those%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20pass%20it%20down%20to%20us%2C%20which%20means%20we%20would%20have%20to%20pass%20it%20down%20to%20our%20brides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdams%20said%20some%20bridal%20stores%20might%20try%20to%20absorb%20the%20costs%2C%20but%20at%20the%20current%20tariff%20rate%2C%20it%20likely%20won't%20be%20feasible.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20might%20instead%20absorb%2050%25%20and%20then%20pass%20the%20other%20half%20on%20to%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComplicating%20the%20situation%20is%20that%20many%20bridal%20gowns%20are%20made-to-order%2C%20meaning%20some%20brides%20have%20already%20picked%20out%20and%20paid%20for%20dresses%20now%20being%20produced%20abroad.%20When%20those%20gowns%20are%20delivered%2C%20they%20could%20be%20hit%20with%20a%20huge%20tariff%20for%20which%20the%20bride%20or%20the%20bridal%20shop%20never%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVanessa%20Gerstner%2C%20whose%20wedding%20is%20this%20September%20in%20Italy%2C%20told%20BI%20she's%20waiting%20for%20a%20dress%20she%20ordered%20in%20November%20to%20arrive%20from%20Australia%20%E2%80%94%20where%20tariffs%20on%20imported%20goods%20are%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20hoping%20that%20I%20won't%20get%20another%20huge%20charge%20on%20top%20of%20what%20I've%20already%20paid%2C%20but%20since%20it%20is%20being%20shipped%20directly%20to%20me%20and%20not%20a%20bridal%20salon%2C%20I%20think%2C%20from%20my%20understanding%2C%20I%20would%20have%20to%20eat%20that%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20additional%20fee%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20terrible%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20compared%20to%20other%20brides%20who%20are%20now%20opting%20for%20cheaper%20dresses%20than%20they%20originally%20planned%20due%20to%20the%20increased%20tariff%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBridal%20consultant%20Alina%20Garza%2C%20who%20works%20at%20One%20Bridal%20in%20Annapolis%2C%20Maryland%2C%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20to%20TikTok%20last%20week%20that%20dress%20designers%20have%20already%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20to%20say%20they'll%20be%20raising%20prices%20by%20up%20to%2020%25.%20Two%20are%20US%20designers%20that%20source%20fabric%20from%20India%20and%20China%2C%20she%20later%20told%20BI%20by%20direct%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20commenter%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20able%20to%20sleep%20over%20this%26quot%3B%20and%20planned%20to%20have%20items%20from%20China%20shipped%20to%20Mexico%2C%20where%20she%20would%20pick%20them%20up.%20Another%20said%20the%20factory%20making%20her%20dress%20has%20paused%20all%20shipments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225704b89e-c0d2-4a55-880c-927706e05c36%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShifting%20production%20out%20of%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20said%20one%20of%20his%20motivations%20for%20the%20tariffs%20is%20to%20encourage%20more%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20But%20while%20big%20bridal%20companies%20are%20considering%20shifting%20production%20out%20of%20China%2C%20they%20aren't%20necessarily%20looking%20at%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20Cook%2C%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavids-bridal-ceo-jim-marcum-optimistic-about-future-after-bankruptcy-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid's%20Bridal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20largest%20wedding%20retailer%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Btariff-proof%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Btariff-resilient%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20part%20because%20it%20has%2036%20design%20and%20production%20facilities%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20and%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20anticipation%20of%20tariffs%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20proactively%20shifting%20its%20production%20out%20of%20China%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20Cook%20said%20the%20company%20has%20lowered%20its%20China-based%20production%20from%2050%25%20of%20its%20total%20just%20several%20months%20ago%20to%2030%25%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20working%20to%20help%20its%20partners%2C%20who%20primarily%20manufacture%20dresses%20in%20China%2C%20shift%20production%20to%20their%20facilities%20in%20countries%20that%20haven't%20been%20hit%20quite%20as%20hard%20by%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Friday%2C%20Cook%20said%20David's%20Bridal%20had%20not%20raised%20prices.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20do%20everything%20in%20our%20power%20not%20to%20pass%20anything%20on%20to%20the%20customer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smaller%20bridal%20shops%20said%20they%20were%20also%20working%20with%20their%20manufacturers%20to%20avoid%20passing%20on%20costs%20to%20brides%2C%20but%20the%20longer%20the%20high%20tariffs%20remain%2C%20the%20harder%20that%20will%20be.%20Still%2C%20they%20said%20many%20bridal%20shops%20now%20have%20plenty%20of%20gowns%20in%20store%20that%20brides%20could%20take%20home%2C%20free%20of%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdams%2C%20who%20owns%20the%20shop%20in%20Louisiana%2C%20said%20it's%20still%20too%20soon%20to%20tell%20how%20severe%20the%20impact%20will%20be%20and%20that%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20cause%20fear%20among%20brides.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20freak%20people%20out%20and%20then%20a%20month%20later%20everything%20goes%20back%20to%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Adams%20is%20also%20concerned%20that%20if%20tariffs%20do%20raise%20prices%2C%20it%20could%20deter%20brides%20from%20visiting%20their%20local%20brick-and-mortar%20bridal%20stores%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20longtime%20fixtures%20on%20their%20local%20main%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20people%20in%20Washington%20will%20give%20a%20little%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20want%20people%20to%20not%20get%20married%20and%20not%20celebrate%20life%20moments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-trump-china-wedding-dresses-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744546202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f98d373fe8d3928362ed02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-trump-china-wedding-dresses-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20wedding%20dresses%20are%20made%20in%20China.%20That%20means%20Trump's%20huge%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20could%20make%20getting%20married%20more%20expensive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessins