-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20routine%20and%20dedication%2C%20Krishna%20acknowledges%20that%20the%20work%20takes%20a%20toll.%20A%20fall%20in%20recent%20years%20left%20him%20with%20persistent%20back%20pain%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20lift%20heavy%20objects%20or%20bend%20for%20long.%20His%20daughters%20now%20help%20him%20with%20cleaning%20work%2C%20but%20even%20with%20their%20assistance%2C%20continuing%20this%20work%20is%20becoming%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%2C%20there%20is%20very%20little%20profit%20in%20rearing%20cows.%20The%20work%20is%20tough%20and%20full%20of%20challenges%E2%80%94you%20have%20to%20be%20present%20at%20all%20times%2C%20give%20them%20food%2C%20bathe%20them%2C%20take%20them%20grazing%2C%20and%20milk%20them.%20It%20requires%20true%20dedication%20and%20affection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20spends%20close%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20every%20month%20on%20fodder%20from%20Sattari%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20the%20machine-cut%20fodder%20spoils%20in%20the%20rain%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20is%20saddened%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20younger%20generation%20has%20little%20interest%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20prefer%20office%20jobs%2C%20especially%20since%20they%E2%80%99ve%20had%20access%20to%20higher%20education.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20us%20working%20hard%20in%20the%20sun%20and%20rain%2C%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20that%20life.%20And%20the%20truth%20is%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20you%20work%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20left%20to%20save%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%20That%20makes%20it%20even%20harder%20to%20convince%20anyone%20to%20continue%20this%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20believes%20fieldwork%20keeps%20a%20person%20healthy.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20when%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20pumps%2C%20we%20used%20ropes%20to%20draw%20water%20from%20wells%E2%80%94it%20was%20hard%20work%20but%20good%20for%20the%20heart%20and%20overall%20health.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Krishna%20says%20he%20is%20truly%20content.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F383592%2Fwildlife-conservation-sharvan-patel-rajasthan-whatsapp-group-save-species-habitats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20cows%20are%20not%20just%20animals%20to%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20like%20family.%20My%20life%20now%20revolves%20around%20them.%20It%20amazes%20me%20how%20deeply%20they%20understand%20and%20respond%20to%20me.%20Not%20a%20single%20day%20goes%20by%20without%20seeing%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20honestly%2C%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20make%20my%20day%20complete.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20hopes%20that%20more%20people%20will%20see%20the%20value%20in%20traditional%20farming%20and%20cow%20rearing%20before%20it%20disappears%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EForgotten%20resource%3A%20The%20fall%20of%20a%20rural%20staple%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20his%20cows%2C%20Krishna%20has%20an%20endless%20supply%20of%20cow%20dung%20%E2%80%93%20a%20resource%20he%20says%20is%20very%20precious.%20During%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20it%20is%20stored%20in%20the%20shed%2C%20while%20in%20other%20seasons%2C%20it%20is%20dried%20and%20used%20as%20manure%20in%